        Clause 40 [<span class="italic">Substitute road services</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0670P0-03489'>
        <a name='S5LV0670P0_20050309_GCR_66'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-william-astor' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0670P0_20050309_GCR_66' title='Link to this speech by Mr William Astor' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
